tachyon.client

Class InStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • tachyon.client.InStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BlockInStream, EmptyBlockInStream, FileInStream

    public abstract class InStream
extends InputStream
    InStream is the base class of input stream for TachyonFile streaming input. To get an instance of this class, one should call the static method getInStream of tachyon.client.TachyonFile, rather than constructing a new instance directly in the client code.

      • seek

        public abstract void seek(long pos)
                   throws IOException
        Sets the stream pointer offset, measured from the beginning of this stream, at which the next read or write occurs. The offset may be set beyond the end of the stream.
        Parameters:
        pos - the offset position, measured in bytes from the beginning of the InStream, at which to set the stream pointer.
        Throws:
        IOException - if pos is less than 0 or if an I/O error occurs.
